towntext = "You stand in the centre of the small town that you've come to call home, the forests surrounding it are full of danger, but without other adventurer's around you're the one best equipped to handle the threats posed by it.\n\nThe town proper had the mainstay inn, which was indeed the place where you mainly stayed when you weren't out in the wilderness. The apothecary always held a good selection of potions to assist you during your battles, and the scent of the herbs and flowers grown there was rather pleasant to boot. Considerably worse smelling was the smithy, but that place was a good source of reliable weapons and armor."
firstmeeting = "As you return to the town, you notice a frail looking cow woman staggering towards you. Her eyes lighting up as she catches sight of your battle-worn attire. \"An adventurer! Please, come with me, I need your assistance urgently.\" She grabs ahold of your arm, though her grip is too feeble to really pull you along. But you comply, the poor woman clearly quite desperate for your help with something. " ;
